# Dart / Flutter

## Structure

- `lib/services/vpn_service.dart` — connect/disconnect orchestration
- `lib/utils/config_parser.dart` — subscription normalization, secure inbound injection
- `lib/utils/link_config_builder.dart` — share-link → JSON
- `lib/providers/vpn_providers.dart` — Riverpod; persist profiles in SharedPreferences

## Patterns

- Use `ConfigParserException` for config errors; `StateError` in VpnService for runtime failures
- Engine switch: disconnect first (`VpnService.setEngine`)
- Subscription fetch **must** use engine-specific User-Agent in `ConfigParser.parseFromUrl`

## Tests required when touching

- `test/config_parser_test.dart` — injection, subscription, proxyOnly, DNS migration
- `test/security_test.dart` — no 7890, 127.0.0.1 bind
- `test/credential_service_test.dart` — credential generation

## Style

- `dart format` / 80-char line length (see `.cursor/settings.json`)
- Minimal diffs; no unrelated refactors
- Full imports in snippets
